&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1629&quot; data-end=&quot;1836&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1631&quot; data-end=&quot;1836&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1631&quot; data-end=&quot;1657&quot;&gt;Engineering Execution:&lt;/strong&gt; Own the end-to-end development, quality, performance, and operational excellence of your teams&#39; components, ensuring deployment in cloud-native environments (e.g., Kubernetes).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
